<paragraph id="D44EBF23A816F110FF5EFE64FDEF988C" blockId="7.[178,1085,408,489]" pageId="7" pageNumber="1368">
Etymology: The species is dedicated to Alexandr Anichtchenko, 
<collectingRegion id="163571C1A816F110FC28FE64FBC998CB" box="[964,1082,408,430]" country="Latvia" name="Daugavpils" pageId="7" pageNumber="1368">Daugavpils</collectingRegion>
