<collectingCountry id="ACE6FFB3A816F110FF5EFE4AFF0698A9" box="[178,245,438,460]" name="Latvia" pageId="7" pageNumber="1368">Latvia</collectingCountry>
, specialist on Lebiinae and other Carabids, who collected the 
<typeStatus id="0B4A0181A816F110FC9AFE4AFC3C98A9" box="[886,975,438,460]" pageId="7" pageNumber="1368">holotype</typeStatus>
and a part of the 
<typeStatus id="0B4A0181A816F110FF1FFE28FEA7988C" box="[243,340,468,489]" pageId="7" pageNumber="1368">paratypes</typeStatus>
of the new species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
